features: 5 ACTION FIGURES with ACCESSORIES: 4 Army Figures with exclusive K9 includes assorted Military gear including machine guns and helmets with night vision goggles. Each figure stands 4'' tall.

REALISTIC FEATURES: Take on any battle with these realistic 1/18 scale figures. Ultra-realistic details encourage realistic role play. Each character has their own distinct look and features to help define their position.

NATURAL ARTICULATION: Each figure is fully poseable with over 10 points of articulation for more realistic play. It's easy to bend their arms and legs to create endless poses for your pretend battle scenes!
PRETEND PLAY: Imaginative play allows kids to explore and express themselves. Join forces and explore a new storyline with the Elite Force Army Ranger figures!
GREAT GIFT: Add an impressive piece to your Military collection. Gather up the troops and combine with other Elite Force items for a more immersive set of figures and vehicles.
body.description: Flush out the enemy with your Army Ranger set. This playset includes a full squad equipped to handled your most advanced missions. Your K9 Dog Handler (code name: Bull) can take to the investigation with the K9 unit (code name: Hans). Set up your sniper (code name: Scopes) up on a high tower to take down enemy fire from afar. Your M240B Gunner (code name: Smoke) and Rifleman (code name: Brass) are ready to move in for close quarters combat, or provides support for Scopes. Each Ranger is ready for action with assorted military gear including machineguns and night-vision goggles. Use the variety of figurines to reenact historical events or use your imagination to create unique battles. The perfect set for kids or collectors!Established in 2012, Sunny Days Entertainment, LLC is comprised of a core group of toy industry veterans with the mission of spreading sunshine through traditional, creative play. Our focus is to enhance the experience for consumers in order to expand children’s imaginations and encourage them to unplug and play. At Sunny Days, each toy is designed with safety in mind. All of our toys are thoroughly tested to meet the highest standards possible. We stand by our superior quality and want to ensure complete satisfaction. If you experience any trouble, please reach out to our team so we can make it right.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars cheap gi joes
reviews.reviewText: Bought these for my son as an alternative for gi joes i had growing up. he loves them, but they arent the most durable. had them since christmas and 2 already broke a leg off trying to get them into some of the vehicles. they are cool for a kid and a good alternative to expensive gi joes. just dont expect them to last as long as the old joes did.
